Information
------------------------------
Highlights of the Velothon Wales event held on 22nd May. With thousands of riders taking part in a mass-ride, alongside a UCI-sanctioned elite race. Cardiff hosts a truly spectacular weekend festival of cycling with tough climbs and a backdrop of historic castles, both routes take in some of Wales' most breathtaking scenery, before riding into the Welsh capital for the finish cheered on by thousands of fans.
